## Vendor Dimension Table

A dedicated vendor dimension table was created to centralize vendor-level metrics and risk classifications.

This approach improves:
- Model clarity
- Risk categorization consistency
- Separation of analytical logic from transactional data

### Risk Dimensions
- Financial Risk: Based on spend concentration
- Operational Risk: Based on overdue performance
- Efficiency Risk: Based on PO fragmentation indicators


# Vendor Risk Assessment

This section evaluates key vendors across three risk dimensions:
- Financial Risk (spend concentration)
- Operational Risk (purchase order delays)
- Efficiency Risk (PO fragmentation)

Risk levels are classified using relative benchmarks derived from the dataset.

